{"code":0,"rows":{"id":36156,"pid":0,"parentPath":"/","level":null,"productId":33,"productName":"超融合HCI","contentId":36199,"name":"【HCI-VN】网口频繁闪断告警。错误码：0x00000814040C000E","sort":null,"status":1,"hideSubset":null,"power":0,"downloadNum":0,"children":null,"createAdminId":"68532","updateAdminId":"14201","createTime":null,"updateTime":"2026-01-15 11:25:46","deleteTime":null,"type":null,"category":null,"content":"<div class=\"mceNonEditable problem-description-box\" contenteditable=\"false\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable firstMceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"*问题描述\" /> <a id=\"menu1\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"问题描述\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"problem-description\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">网口频繁闪断告警</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\" contenteditable=\"false\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"告警信息\" /> <a id=\"menu2\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"告警信息\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\"><img src=\"/_static/202601/ae3bf21eea1611f084e6fa163e0bdd14.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\" contenteditable=\"false\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"有效排查步骤\" /> <a id=\"menu3\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"有效排查步骤\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>登录对应主机，可以使用ethtool 查看对应网口接线状态</p>\n<p><img src=\"/_static/202601/696468d9ea1811f084e6fa163e0bdd14.png\" /></p>\n<p>多次查看，如果变为no状态，则说明存在闪断</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2.或者查看/sf/log/today/kernel.log 搜索告警网口，查看日志中是否出现down相关的日志</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>3.如果是排查历史告警，可以查看/sf/log/vn-blackbox/today/LOG_ipaddr.txt 黑盒记录</p>\n<p>找到告警时间点附近，观察对应网口上是否出现NO-CARRIER，DOWN的状态</p>\n<p><img src=\"/_static/202601/e3463101ea1811f084e6fa163e0bdd14.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\" contenteditable=\"false\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"根因\" /> <a id=\"menu4\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"根因\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">网口在无操作的情况下，频繁down/up，触发告警</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable problem-description-box\" contenteditable=\"false\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"*解决方案\" /> <a id=\"menu5\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"解决方案\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"problem-description\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>按优先级依次处理</p>\n<p>1.插拔光模块或者网线，可能是接触不良</p>\n<p>2.更换光模块或者网线，可能是不适配导致</p>\n<p>3.可能是网卡故障，可以查看/sf/log/today/kernel.log